room_title: Escape room "Great Aunt Myrtle Ethrington (GAME)" by The Cryptic Room in Omaha
room_address: 523 S Main St Council Bluffs, IA 51503
room_description: Your Great Aunt Myrtle Ethrington was an eccentric woman who loved games and puzzles. You received a letter from her lawyer recently informing you that Myrtle has passed away. Since she had no children of her own, her final wishes were that only those in her family that will continue to carry on her love of games and puzzles will inherit the fortune that she had secretly stashed away. Are you up to her challenge?
